responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "CE660EB44DC6BACE0EAE9BBCBCDA758E", "Where once we met to howl at the moons, I shall await. Gather the Stones of Tura\'Madu that rest with graves or are enveloped in the spirits of our noble warhounds. Place the stones within the ancient round and I shall speak to thee.")
name: CSQ_DD_0068_TSS_CaptainsJournal_42
